  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2021-06-24",
    "date": "2021-08-03T14:55:29Z",
    "text": "Lead-Free America Bonds Act of 2021\n\nThis bill allows issuers of qualified lead drinking water service line bonds a credit for interest payments under such bonds. The bill defines qualified lead drinking water service line bond as any bond issue (other than a private activity bond) if 100% of the available project proceeds of such issue are used to replace lead components of one or more eligible public water systems that are not lead free."
